member.name: CERT_HASHED_URL
member.summary: The CERT_HASHED_URL structure contains a hashed URL.

member.name: CERT_HASHED_URL.HashAlgorithm
member.summary: A structure that specifies the hash algorithm used to create the URL hash.

member.name: CERT_HASHED_URL.Hash
member.summary: A CRYPT_HASH_BLOB structure that contains the hash value.

member.name: CERT_HASHED_URL.pwszUrl
member.summary: The address of a null-terminated Unicode string that contains the URL. This member is optional for biometric data and may be NULL.
